OL,3,CHospital declares stands down critical
OL,4,Cincident
OL,6,FDerriford Hospital in Plymouth has
OL,7,Fstood down a critical incident it
OL,8,Fdeclared for the fifth time in 2024.
OL,10,FThe measure, which was brought in at
OL,11,F8am on 4 April, is the highest state
OL,12,Fof alert for a hospital and means that
OL,13,Fadditional steps are taken to ensure
OL,14,Fpatient safety.
OL,16,FThe NHS trust that runs the site says
OL,17,Fit has now stood down the measure but
OL,18,Fhas asked people to only turn up to
OL,19,Fthe emergency department if in a
OL,20,Fserious or life-threatening condition.
