OL,3,CHospital declares stands down critical
OL,4,Cincident
OL,6,FIt was announced due to increased
OL,7,Foperational pressures and IT issues
OL,8,Faffecting the hospital's 'key clinical
OL,9,Fsystems'.
OL,11,FIt added that people attending A&E who
OL,12,Fdo not have emergency or life-
OL,13,Fthreatening conditions may be sent to
OL,14,Fother healthcare services, as the
OL,15,Femergency department is 'very full'.
