OL,3,CHospital declares stands down critical
OL,4,Cincident
OL,6,FStaff say anyone who is unwell should
OL,7,Finstead call NHS 111 or use NHS 111
OL,8,Fonline, where they may be provided
OL,9,Fwith advice or redirected to other
OL,10,Fsites, such as the minor injury units
OL,11,Fin Tavistock and Kingsbridge.
OL,13,FBut University Hospitals Plymouth NHS
OL,14,FTrust added that those with a 'very
OL,15,Fserious or life-threatening emergency'
OL,16,Fshould still attend A&E.
