OL,3,CHospital declares stands down critical
OL,4,Cincident
OL,6,FThe hospital has declared a critical
OL,7,Fincident five times since the start of
OL,8,Fthe year, with the first incident
OL,9,Fbeing announced just five days into
OL,10,F2024. At that time, staff said it was
OL,11,Fdue to higher numbers of people
OL,12,Fattending A&E over the previous three
OL,13,Fdays.
OL,15,FThey declared a second incident later
OL,16,Fin January, which lasted for eight
OL,17,Fdays, and a third in February, which
OL,18,Flasted for three days, after high
OL,19,Fnumbers of people with the flu
OL,20,Fstretched capacity at Derriford
OL,21,FHospital.
