OL,3,CHospital declares stands down critical
OL,4,Cincident
OL,6,FStaff then declared a fourth critical
OL,7,Fincident on the afternoon of Sunday 10
OL,8,FMarch due to 'high occupancy' in the
OL,9,Fhospital.
OL,11,FWhere to go for treatment:
OL,13,FThe trust said in a statement that
OL,14,F"colleagues are working hard to
OL,15,Fprioritise patients based on their
OL,16,Fclinical need and move patients to the
OL,17,Fright place for them as soon as
OL,18,Fpossible".
